## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-124">Следует всегда закрывать экземпляр класса <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> с помощью метода <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.Close%2A> по окончании работы с этим объектом.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-124">You should always close a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> instance by calling <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.Close%2A> when finished working with it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-125">Потенциально это позволяет освободить системные ресурсы быстрее.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-125">This allows system resources to potentially be freed sooner.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-126">После вызова метода <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message.CreateBufferedCopy%2A> для создания буфера сообщения и анализа сообщения с использованием метода <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.CreateMessage%2A> при попытке закрытия буфера с помощью этого метода будет создано исключение <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-126">If you have called <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message.CreateBufferedCopy%2A> to create a message buffer of a message, and inspected the message using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.CreateMessage%2A>, you will get a <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> when you attempt to close the buffer using this method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-127">Чтобы избежать этой проблемы, необходимо повторно создать сообщение из буфера перед закрытием буфера.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-127">To avoid this problem, you need to recreate the message from the buffer before closing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-128">Пример кода см. в образце кода, предоставленном для предыдущего сценария.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-128">See the code sample in the Example section for a demonstration of the previous scenario and a way to resolve this problem.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-129">В следующем примере показано, как правильно закрыть буфер сообщения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-129">The following example demonstrates how to properly close a message buffer.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void AfterReceiveReply(ref Message reply, object correlationState)  
{  
    // Create the buffer  
    MessageBuffer buffer = reply.CreateBufferedCopy(13000);  
    // Inspect the response (for example, extract the body contents)  
    Message thisReply = buffer.CreateMessage();  
    XmlDictionaryReader reader = thisReply.GetReaderAtBodyContents();  
    StringBuilder info = new StringBuilder();  
    XmlWriter writer = XmlWriter.Create(info);  
    writer.WriteNode(reader, true);  
    writer.Close();  
    // Resolution:  Re-create the message from the buffer before  
    // closing.  
    reply = buffer.CreateMessage();  
    // You can close the buffer after the message has been recreated.  
    buffer.Close();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-130">}</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-130">}</span></span>

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-165">Данная функция использует двоичный кодировщик вместо кодировщика UTF-8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-165">This function uses a binary encoder instead of a UTF-8 encoder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-166">Таким образом, выполнить прямое преобразование объекта <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> в объект <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> невозможно.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-166">Therefore, you cannot directly convert from a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> to a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b4bb-167">В следующем примере показано, как обойти эту проблему.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b4bb-167">The code in the example section shows how to work around this problem.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
private byte[] ConvertMessageToByteArray(ref Message message)   
{  
....//Memory stream that contains the message  
....MemoryStream stream = new MemoryStream();  
....//Create an XmlWriter to serialize the message into a byte array  
....XmlWriterSettings settings = new XmlWriterSettings();  
....settings.Encoding = System.Text.Encoding.UTF8;  
....XmlWriter writer = XmlWriter.Create(stream, settings);  
....//Copy the message into a buffer   
....//Note: This call changes the original message's state  
....MessageBuffer buffer = message.CreateBufferedCopy(int.MaxValue);  
....//Create a copy of the message  
....message = buffer.CreateMessage();  
....//Serialize the message to the XmlWriter   
....message.WriteMessage(writer);  
....//Recreate the message   
....message = buffer.CreateMessage();  
....//Flush the contents of the writer so that the stream gets updated  
....writer.Flush();  
....stream.Flush();  
....//Convert the stream to an array  
....byte[] retval = stream.ToArray();  
    return retval;  
}  
```
